overview:
DaPolonia is where you can find the best Polish handicrafts. We offer exquisite glass Christmas ornaments, extraordinary Baltic amber jewelry made by award winning artists, traditional hand made Polish wooden boxes and unique wooden picture frames.

DaPolonia.com has the great honor to be working with the award winning Krakow’s artists who create the Krakow Nativities, a unique Krakow tradition, created only in Krakow. Our artists take part in the yearly Krakow Nativity Competition organized for over 70 years by Krakow Historical Museum. Each of our Krakow’s Nativities is one of a kind. Our artists never do two of the same.

Many of our tree ornaments are one of a kind made by a few chosen glass artists whose work has been featured in a museum show.

DaPolonia.com caters to the discriminating art lovers and collectors who will be satisfied by nothing but the best of glass Christmas ornaments, wooden boxes, picture frames, amber jewelry and Krakow nativities.
